Makes: 3 skewersIngredients:2.5ml ( tsp) cajun spice clove of crushed garlic10ml (2 tsp) crushed onionPinch of cayenne pepper9 deveined and shelled prawns, with tails on60ml (4 tbsp) porter beer 30ml (2 tbsp) olive oilMethod:1) Mix cajun spice, crushed garlic, onion and cayenne pepper in a bowl.2) Evenly sprinkle the mixture onto the prawns and marinate for 3 hours.3) Pour beer over the prawns and marinate for another 30 minutes.4) Place 3 prawns per skewer, baste with olive oil and grill for 3-4 minutes on each side.5) Serve immediately.